	   <tr><td colspan=2>Goto google.com and in the search and type in Concert Hall Everquest.<br><br>Concert Hall is the best (IMHO) site about bards. A must have bookmark for all bards.  Here is the link:  <a href="http://www.attcanada.net/~reaper/" target=_new>http://www.attcanada.net/~reaper/</a><br><br>As to your drum question each instument is a skill that you learn.<br><br>Percussion (Drum) at 5<br>Sting (Guitar) at 8<br>Brass (Horn) at 11<br>Wind (Flute) at 14<br><br>These intrument skills HAVE TO HAVE AT LEAST 1 training point put into them once you reach the required level otherwise when you goto equip it it wont allow it.<br><br>The Concert hall has a listing of songs and what instrument ENCHANCE them.<br><br>For example when playing Selo's equip the drum and youll run faster than normal.   Now remember that when equipping an instrument thats the only thing you can have no shield or anything else.  And the only way to raise the selected instruments skill is to play that song with the instrument and youll see the skill go up.<br><br>For example when I wanna increase my percussion i just play selos in town and equipp the drum and go afk for a while and poof its done.<br><br>So goto the concert hall and research.  <br><br>Acousticia<br>12 Bard<br>Erollisi Marr<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
