	   <tr><td colspan=2>As most bards know, changing your instruments and weapons can be a pain in the middle of a battle.<br>Here's a tip.<br>In your inventory, hold down melee 1, melee 2, and some inventory slots until they become hotbuttons.  Place these hot buttons on the same page, and voila!  <br>You can now change inst. and weapons very quickly.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
